<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>不是本地人带路都找不到的隐世农庄</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>开业3年凭口碑，登上美食榜TOP1</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>山泉水粥底火锅是招牌主打</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>锅底清甜、食材鲜、口感嫩、匠心制作</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200904/7ea63ba9af6942288b00589341ed608c.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>·招牌山泉粥底火锅，到店必点·</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200904/cdac695c90e544f68986e0d6e9826346.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
